title: Pie Maker Beef Cheese and Bacon
directions: Soften onion in a fry pan with a tablespoon of oil
Add Bacon and fry until cooked
Add Mince and fry until cooked
Stir in Gravy Pouches, then set aside
Cut Bases and Tops from the Pastry Sheets
Place Pastry Bottoms in a pie maker and fill with mixture
Top with Cheese and add Pastry Lids
Cook for 15-20 minutes or until done
